---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../config";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<style>
				.container {
					max-width: 800px;
					margin: 0 auto;
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.header {
					text-align: center;
					font-size: 36px;
					font-weight: bold;
					margin-bottom: 20px;
				}
				.subheader {
					text-align: center;
					font-size: 18px;
					margin-bottom: 40px;
				}
				.section {
					margin-bottom: 40px;
				}
				.section-title {
					font-size: 24px;
					font-weight: bold;
					margin-bottom: 20px;
				}

				.experience-container {
					display: flex;
					flex-wrap: wrap;
					justify-content: center;
				}

				.experience-item {
					width: 100%;
					padding: 20px;
					text-align: left;
					background-color: #f2f2f2;
					border-radius: 10px;
					box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px #ccc;
				}

				.job-title {
					font-size: 20px;
					margin-top: 0px;
					margin-bottom: 10px;
				}

				.company-name {
					font-size: 18px;
					margin-top: 0px;
					margin-bottom: 10px;
					color: #999;
				}

				.job-dates {
					font-size: 14px;
					margin-top: 0;
					margin-bottom: 10px;
					color: #bbb;
				}

				.job-description {
					font-size: 16px;
				}
				.skill-category {
					display: flex;
					flex-wrap: wrap;

					align-items: center;
					height: 100%;
				}
				.skill-category-title {
					font-weight: bold;
					text-align: center;
					margin-bottom: 12px;
					display: flex;
					width: 100%;
				}
				.skill-bubble {
					background-color: lightgray;
					color: black;
					padding: 10px;
					margin: 3px;
					border-radius: 50px;
					display: flex;
					align-items: center;
					justify-content: center;
					min-width: fit-content;
					height: 10px;
					animation: bubble-in 1s ease-out forwards;
				}

				@keyframes bubble-in {
					from {
						transform: scale(0);
					}
					to {
						transform: scale(1);
					}
				}
			</style>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="header">Andr√©s Marrugo</div>
				<div class="subheader">Frontend Developer</div>
				<div class="section">
					<div class="section-title">Resume</div>
					<p>
						Over the last 3 years, I've been working as a web
						developer. I've been using React and some of its
						essential libraries, like React Router, Redux, React
						Query, Axios, Material UI, Ant Design, TypeScript, and
						React Hook Forms. My daily workflow involves using Git
						for version control and work in team. I'm also
						experienced with Docker and popular cloud services like
						Azure, AWS, and Google Cloud. I've had the opportunity
						to work on several projects for different clients, using
						the Scrum methodology and issue tracking tools such as
						Jira and Trello. I'm confident in my ability to bring
						success to any project I work on, and I'm always eager
						to learn and grow as a developer.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="section">
					<div class="section-title">Skills</div>
					<div class="skill-category">
						<div class="skill-category-title">
							React and its Ecosystem
						</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">React</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">React Router</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Redux</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">React Query</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Axios</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Material UI</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Ant Design</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">TypeScript</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">React Hook Forms</div>
					</div>
					<div class="skill-category">
						<div class="skill-category-title">
							Tools and Technologies
						</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Git</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Jira</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Trello</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Docker</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Azure</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">AWS</div>
						<div class="skill-bubble">Google Cloud</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="section">
					<h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>
					<div class="experience-container">
						<div class="experience-item">
							<h3 class="job-title">Fronted Developer</h3>
							<h4 class="company-name">Lean Tech</h4>
							<p class="job-dates">
								November 2019 - September 2022
							</p>
							<p class="job-description">
								During my time at Lean Tech, I had the
								opportunity to work on the implementation of
								various software products for international
								clients in the freight transportation industry
								in the USA. As a frontend developer, I played a
								crucial role in ensuring the successful delivery
								of these projects. Collaborating closely with
								the team, I worked towards a common goal of
								delivering high-quality software solutions that
								met the needs and expectations of our clients.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
